-ian-3156-ian-3087-ian-3193", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "Brazil, IAN, 1980s-1990s", "traits": "IAN 3156 and 3087 have good girth growth. Variable characteristics by clone", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "1500-1800 kg/ha/year", "growing_notes": "IAN 2880 and 3156 have establishment potential. Part of Amazonian genetic base expansion.", "availability": "Import through germplasm programs", "sort_order": 32}, {"name": "IRCA 18, IRCA 111, IRCA 130", "slug": "irca-18-irca-111-irca-130", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "Côte d''Ivoire, IRCA, 1970s-1980s", "traits": "Active/rapid metabolism clones. IRCA 130 highest productivity. Good radial vegetative growth (2.9 cm/year). Well-balanced physiological profile", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "1700-2400 kg/ha/year (high productivity)", "growing_notes": "Recommended for 5-10% of area for detailed evaluation. High-yielding modern clones. IRCA 111 parent in breeding programs.", "availability": "Import through international programs", "sort_order": 33}, {"name": "RRIC 100, RRIC 110, RRIC 121", "slug": "rric-100-rric-110-rric-121", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "Sri Lanka, RRIC, 1980s-1990s", "traits": "RRIC 121 outstanding growth and timber. RRIC 110 susceptible to Corynespora. RRIC 100 moderate performance", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "1700-2000 kg/ha/year", "growing_notes": "Sri Lankan clones very suitable for Kerala''s similar monsoon climate. RRIC 121 recommended for timber.", "availability": "Can be imported to India", "sort_order": 34}, {"name": "RRIC 102", "slug": "rric-102", "lineage_type": "hybrid", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "Sri Lanka, RRIC, 1980s-1990s", "traits": "Vigorous, very high bark thickness, satisfactory growth, slightly yellow latex", "flesh_fruit": "", "yield_notes": "1800 kg/ha/year first 7 years", "growing_notes": "Group I recommendation in Sri La